{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"Pusty element","mdn_url":"/pl/docs/Glossary/Empty_element","locale":"pl","native":"Polski","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>Pusty element</strong> to&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Element\">element <small>(en-US)</small></a> HTML, SVG&nbsp;lub MathML który&nbsp;<strong>nie może</strong> mieć żadnych węzłów dziecięcych (tj. elementów zagnieżdżonych lub węzłów tekstowych).</p>\n\n<p>Specyfikacje&nbsp;<a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML</a>, <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG2/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG</a>&nbsp;i <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/MathML3/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MathML</a> określają bardzo dokładnie, co każdy element może zawierać. Wiele kombinacji nie ma znaczenia semantycznego, na przykład element&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/audio\"><code>&lt;audio&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> zagnieżdżony wewnątrz elementu&nbsp;<a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/hr\"><code>&lt;hr&gt;</code></a>.</p>\n\n<p>W HTML, użycie znacznika zamykającego na pustym elemencie jest zazwyczaj nieważne. Na przykład,&nbsp;<code>&lt;input type=\"text\"&gt;&lt;/input&gt;</code> jest nieprawidłowy.</p>\n\n<p>Puste elementy w HTML są następujące:</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/area\"><code>&lt;area&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/base\"><code>&lt;base&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/br\"><code>&lt;br&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/col\"><code>&lt;col&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/embed\"><code>&lt;embed&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/hr\"><code>&lt;hr&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/img\"><code>&lt;img&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/keygen\"><code>&lt;keygen&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>(HTML 5.2 Projekt usunięty)</li>\n <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/link\"><code>&lt;link&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/meta\"><code>&lt;meta&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/param\"><code>&lt;param&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/source\"><code>&lt;source&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"Pusty element to element (en-US) HTML, SVG lub MathML który nie może mieć żadnych węzłów dziecięcych (tj. elementów zagnieżdżonych lub węzłów tekstowych).","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Leeres Element","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Empty element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Elemento vacío","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Élément vide","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Empty element (空要素)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"빈 요소","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Пустой элемент","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"空元素","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Empty element","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/glossary/empty_element","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/glossary/empty_element/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pl/docs/Glossary","title":"Glossary"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Glossary/Empty_element","title":"Pusty element"}],"pageTitle":"Pusty element - Glossary | MDN","noIndexing":false}}